# AgentConfig Module

## Overview

Agent Identity System supports Soul, Profession, and Model configuration per agent

## Goals

- **G1** — Agent Identity System supports Soul, Profession, and Model configuration per agent

## Key Architecture Decisions

- **A1** — Agent Instance Lifecycle

## Key Designs

- **D1** — AgentInstance & Soul Rendering
- **D2** — Profession Registry (v2)
- **D3** — Architect Soul v2 — Code Verification & Quality Constraints

